<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Privacy Policy — sLab</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
    body { font-family:'Inter',sans-serif; background:#0a0a0a; color:#d4d4d4; min-height:100vh; padding:40px 24px; }
    .wrap { max-width:720px; margin:0 auto; }
    .logo { text-align:center; margin-bottom:32px; }
    .logo a { font-size:24px; font-weight:600; color:#fff; text-decoration:none; }
    .logo a span { color:#c9a848; }
    h1 { font-size:28px; font-weight:700; color:#fff; margin-bottom:8px; }
    .updated { font-size:12px; color:#737373; margin-bottom:32px; }
    h2 { font-size:16px; font-weight:600; color:#fff; margin:28px 0 10px; }
    p, li { font-size:14px; line-height:1.8; color:#a3a3a3; margin-bottom:12px; }
    ul { padding-left:20px; margin-bottom:12px; }
    a { color:#c9a848; }
    .back { display:inline-block; margin-top:32px; font-size:13px; color:#737373; text-decoration:none; }
    .back:hover { color:#c9a848; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="logo"><a href="/"><span>s</span>Lab</a></div>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: April 2026</p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Account information:</strong> Name, email address, business name, and subdomain when you sign up.</li>
      <li><strong>Content:</strong> Files, images, videos, text, and other content you upload to the platform.</li>
      <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> Pages visited, features used, IP address, browser type, and device information.</li>
      <li><strong>Payment data:</strong> Processed securely through PayPal. We do not store credit card numbers.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To provide, maintain, and improve the Service.</li>
      <li>To communicate with you about your account, updates, and support.</li>
      <li>To process payments and manage your subscription.</li>
      <li>To detect and prevent fraud or abuse.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Data Storage</h2>
    <p>Your content is stored on Linode Object Storage (Akamai) in the US. Account and configuration data is stored in MongoDB databases. We use encryption (AES-256-GCM) for sensitive credentials and secrets.</p>

    <h2>4. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share data with:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Service providers:</strong> Cloud hosting (Linode/Akamai), email delivery (Zoho), payment processing (PayPal, Stripe) — only as necessary to operate the Service.</li>
      <li><strong>Legal requirements:</strong> When required by law, court order, or to protect our rights.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. AI Processing</h2>
    <p>The platform includes AI-powered features (content generation, design agents). Your prompts and brand context are sent to third-party AI providers (Anthropic, local models) to generate responses. We do not use your content to train AI models.</p>

    <h2>6. Cookies</h2>
    <p>We use essential cookies for authentication and session management (scoped to <code>.madladslab.com</code>). We do not use third-party tracking cookies or advertising pixels.</p>

    <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of your data at any time.</li>
      <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request account and data deletion. We will remove your data within 30 days, except where retention is required by law.</li>
      <li><strong>Export:</strong> Export your assets and content via the admin panel.</li>
      <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Update your account information through the admin settings.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>8. Data Retention</h2>
    <p>Active accounts: data retained for the life of the account. Cancelled accounts: data retained for 30 days after cancellation, then permanently deleted. Free preview accounts inactive for 90+ days may be purged.</p>

    <h2>9. Security</h2>
    <p>We implement industry-standard security measures including encrypted secrets, HTTPS everywhere, sandboxed tenant isolation, and access controls. However, no system is 100% secure — you are responsible for maintaining the security of your login credentials.</p>

    <h2>10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy as our practices evolve. Material changes will be communicated via email or in-platform notice. Continued use after changes constitutes acceptance.</p>

    <h2>11. Contact</h2>
    <p>Privacy questions? Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@madladslab.com">support@madladslab.com</a>.</p>

    <a href="/" class="back">&larr; Back to home</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
